The Judge has not shifted his position for a long while now . 
He holds his watch in his left hand , but clutched in such a manner that you cannot see the dial plate . 
You hear the ticking of his watch his breath you do not hear . 
A most refreshing slumber , doubtless ! And yet , the Judge cannot be asleep . 
A cautious man is proverbially said to sleep with one eye open . 
But not with both for this were heedlessness ! No , no ! Judge Pyncheon cannot be asleep . 
